From: 
To: 
Cc: 
Subject: Maxwell - Telephone Conference Tomorrow 
Date: Thu, 21 Oct 2021 00:17:58 +0000 
Attachments: 2021.10.19_Order re_October 21_Teleconference.pdf 
I know Bobbi Sternheim emailed you earlier about the telephone conference being held by Judge Nathan tomorrow at 
noon. I just wanted to follow up in case you had any questions and make sure that you have all the information you 
need. The Court emailed the parties that the phone number for the defendant for tomorrow's conference is 
tith access code-. I'm attaching the Court's order on this, which provides the separate dial-in for members 
of the press and the public. Please let us know if you have any questions. 
Thanks so much, 
ssistantUnited States Attorney
